Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE in conjunction with Raine & Horne Commercial is pleased to offer 4-8 Sylvania Way to market for lease. Current tenant Interpod is relocating at end of calendar year 2021 and the buildings will be available for occupation from 1 January 2022.

The subject property offers two large freestanding office/warehouse buildings with ample parking and hardstand on an expansive landscaped 6.48-hectare site.

Located walking distance from Niagara train station the property enjoys close proximity to the major road networks and is surrounded by household names such as Australia Post, Sara Lee/McCain Foods and Scholastic.

Key Features
+ Flexible offering from 3,000sqm to 9,950sqm across two buildings, can be leased individually or in-one line.
+ Offers considered for short-term leases (Min area 1,000sqm) for 2022 calendar year. 
+ High clearance clearspan warehouse with multiple roller doors, docks and expansive awnings
+ Refurbished office, kitchen and bathrooms to building 1
+ 4km from the M1 Motorway
+ Walking distance to Niagara Train station
+ Ample on-site car parking
+ Available for occupation from January 2022

For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact the exclusive marketing agents CBRE or Raine & Horne Commercial
